{"tid":478824,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍緊拖但另一半唔公開嘅你請唔好再埋怨！","createTime":"2017-11-24T12:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T06:46:20.000Z","uid":431,"like":69,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a7047ab4054aa8ebe8406b9d6b56b73377fbb967","tid":478824,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"你去釣魚，如果俾你釣到條鯨魚，你會大大聲同人講<br />\n但如果釣到條沙甸魚，你會唔會同人講啊？<br />\n唔係話你係沙甸魚！只係你唔係佢心目中嗰條魚啫～<br />\n有邊個拍緊拖唔想人知？唔係話要瘋狂放閃<br />\n真係愛你直頭想射尿上你身話俾全世界知&quot;你係我嘅&quot;咁霸地盤啦！<br />\n邊會人哋拍緊拖成日話自己無拍講乜都答哪有女/哪有仔啊！<br />\n怪就怪你自己條件唔好，所以對方先唔想俾人知佢同個咁低級嘅人一齊<br />\n怪你老豆老母生得你咁柒你食到自己咁肥<br />\n唔好怨人哋，係人都鍾意靚嘢，溝到男女神仲唔公諸於世想人羨慕咩<br />\n唔好再呃自己係正常樣，你只係一個僥倖有拖拍嘅柒頭<img src=\"https://forumd.hkgolden.com/faces/lomore/hoho.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforumd.hkgolden.com%2Ffaces%2Flomore%2Fhoho.gif&h=3b1dfe6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f29816275e5b7d5fb1585fffb15b25337c6d2365","tid":478824,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00c4709aef1a152250dab454d55b6334b292d051","tid":478824,"uid":87506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"兩樣野之間有等號？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8d10bbc7d4174ed2b80ea16ec914a3082a6c68","tid":478824,"uid":86037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad4904a4f311f7f1e6e2960a145576e8d73eb5c","tid":478824,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:00:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc8516d58276950c9cfa109bf92dad212e24f1a0","tid":478824,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"9cd4b2425646771bf4d5409f73ad42593eab29db","tid":478824,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy